{"tid":1709654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警襲畢打街 中環人匿置地防空洞","createTime":"2019-11-12T02:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T04:55:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7a7a5d6973152470a14d65bf505727a923de8b","tid":1709654,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191112/CMDNCZ5OX3X5IK5O3SZM6DWU4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191112%2FCMDNCZ5OX3X5IK5O3SZM6DWU4M%2F&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=338811f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191112%2FCMDNCZ5OX3X5IK5O3SZM6DWU4M%2F&h=9f9f3a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191112/CMDNCZ5OX3X5IK5O3SZM6DWU4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n警襲畢打街 中環人匿置地防空洞<br />\n<br />\n【全城煙淚】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網民號召「三罷」，中環、銅鑼灣及旺角等商業中心昨午起都有大批群眾聚集，用雜物堵塞主要道路。警方由中午至晚上不斷發射催淚彈，由中區的高級商場如置地廣場到油麻地平民小商舖，都受催淚煙霧影響，商業運作變相癱瘓。警方昨晚表示，全日多區共拘捕逾260人。醫管局稱，昨日共99人送院，年齡介乎4個月至83歲。<br />\n<br />\n記者︰黃翠儀 羅智堅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/WrmEQ6HU7r20jcmTjM2HUJww74Y=/802x535/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/6QVVX3CKZUQCPXJR66IQRBLV5Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FWrmEQ6HU7r20jcmTjM2HUJww74Y%3D%2F802x535%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F6QVVX3CKZUQCPXJR66IQRBLV5Y.gif&h=e155eccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】催淚煙籠罩行車道，置地廣場成為途人避難所。路透社<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各區260人被捕 99人傷<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：子彈卡脊椎 需割右腎1/3肝<br />\n<br />\n數百人戴上口罩中午12時起在畢打街與德輔道中十字路的行路上聚集，大批防暴警員到場。示威者不斷高聲指罵「強姦犯，殺人犯」，警員警告：「唔好聚集，返工嘅返工，食飯嘅食飯。」其間警員突衝前制服一名男子，又向四周的人噴胡椒噴劑。至12時45分，警員在畢打街發射催淚彈，催淚煙籠罩行車道，無防護裝備的途人爭相逃入置地廣場，催淚煙亦湧進商場內。高級商場變成避難所，大批市民被煙熏而不適，甚至嘔吐，急救員在場為市民洗眼。<br />\n<br />\n裝甲車警︰市民暴徒「一視同仁」<br />\n<br />\n下午1時，一批人重新走出畢打街，高舉「光復香港，時代革命」旗幟，組成傘陣與警對峙。1時半，防暴警再次發射多枚催淚彈，又在德輔道中向市民、記者噴胡椒噴劑，立法會議員許智𥧌亦被噴中。有防暴警向畢打街天橋發射橡膠子彈，一名女士被擊中。<br />\n<br />\n下午2時，警員撤走後，人群再湧出馬路，人數越來越多，有人在德輔道中、干諾道中及皇后大道中用雜物設路障，多輛巴士被噴上「我以死者之名，懇請你罷工」字句。美心的玻璃大門被打爛，牆身噴上「放棄美心」字句。雲咸街中銀分行玻璃被打碎，砵典乍街中銀分行被縱火。下午3時40分，防暴警到場，在德輔道中又發射催淚彈，並清理路障。<br />\n<br />\n中環部份群眾傍晚遊行到銅鑼灣，在崇光百貨外軒尼詩道設路障，防暴警多次發射催淚彈。有人質問警方為何不舉黑旗就發射催淚彈，被數十警衝前包圍，有警員用警棍打他手部，並向其面部噴椒，他最後獲釋。警方其後又截查市民及拘捕多人，記者拍攝時被警員不斷喝罵。警方又在怡和街施放多枚催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n在旺角，由中午起示威者多次用雜物堵塞彌敦道及亞皆老街的十字路口，多輛巴士擋風玻璃被噴漆。<br />\n<br />\n下午3時半，水炮車及銳武裝甲車突然到達彌敦道及亞皆老街交界，數次射水清場。有裝甲車警員向在場市民大叫，不分市民、暴徒「一視同仁」。其後防暴警發射催淚彈驅散。<br />\n<br />\n其後有十多名穿上食環署黃色背心的「義工」到場清理路障。記者追問他們身份未獲回應。警員又突然喝罵在巴士站等車的一對母女，指進入了封鎖線，女兒受驚大哭，警員指斥該母親「唔識教女」。下午近6時，示威者與防暴警於彌敦道及登打士街交界對峙，有黑衣人投擲汽油彈，警方發射多輪催淚彈，彌敦道煙霧瀰漫，途人爭相躲避。有黑衣人燃點雜物作路障，也有電箱起火爆炸。華潤堂旺角分店被掟磚。<br />\n<br />\n晚上7時40分，水炮車在彌敦道一帶噴射催淚水劑，防暴警再向前推進，發射多枚催淚彈。一名的士司機疑被示威者毆打，頭部流血，的士被打爆擋風玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時，近百名示威者在朗豪坊附近設置傘陣，焚燒紙箱。一名男子與示威者發生爭執被圍毆，警方9時半趕到發射多枚催淚彈，示威者四散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/QzLAJ9ANxbfToOBzpAQ_ynibgkc=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CZKL6R3JTYAKRAXI4LQKB7CI6I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FQzLAJ9ANxbfToOBzpAQ_ynibgkc%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCZKL6R3JTYAKRAXI4LQKB7CI6I.gif&h=18fbc66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】大批市民響應快閃行動，早上於中環聚集。張志華攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/UVrKsGMlY5BXG9ibCsMF30VamJU=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ZHCEUBXPUT7ZICIXVKAWHVJFOU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FUVrKsGMlY5BXG9ibCsMF30VamJU%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZHCEUBXPUT7ZICIXVKAWHVJFOU.gif&h=7ed35dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】中午防暴警在畢打街發射催淚彈驅散。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/s80EbrFkNO4rQTmnIlrHO9HwYWQ=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/LWYYIAOSNRECC564DKLHE6SA3Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fs80EbrFkNO4rQTmnIlrHO9HwYWQ%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FLWYYIAOSNRECC564DKLHE6SA3Y.gif&h=b23fc01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【中環】有防暴警近距離向記者施胡椒噴劑。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/62gXP0cN40Ba303ndLH0p3Yf56Q=/802x595/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/7P7O3XZ3Z56XAEBMHBKD4W2LDA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F62gXP0cN40Ba303ndLH0p3Yf56Q%3D%2F802x595%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F7P7O3XZ3Z56XAEBMHBKD4W2LDA.gif&h=26b183e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【旺角】警方晚上再於旺角以水炮車橫掃，街道留下大量泡沫。許頌明攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ETlL5P-2fwL_vi19Nvq06OR6Lc8=/802x595/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ZQHI7GFVAFXZF7XEUAV7MLD2I4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FETlL5P-2fwL_vi19Nvq06OR6Lc8%3D%2F802x595%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZQHI7GFVAFXZF7XEUAV7MLD2I4.gif&h=6269ab08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【旺角】一名男子疑與現場人士爭執，被人群包圍毆打。謝榮耀攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/j8wKiAmTh1P8elGAlL6rt3HZ4Dk=/802x595/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/3JNIW3VZGSSDF6ESN2FIU6MJCY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fj8wKiAmTh1P8elGAlL6rt3HZ4Dk%3D%2F802x595%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F3JNIW3VZGSSDF6ESN2FIU6MJCY.gif&h=cc707c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【銅鑼灣】防暴警驅趕行人路上的市民，其間向急救員方向擎槍。王子俊攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/idqaBXjG4C0jDmskFaAUMgaGp4E=/802x595/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/PPTHJHLCC6DAI4MXOWKSDCUOII.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FidqaBXjG4C0jDmskFaAUMgaGp4E%3D%2F802x595%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FPPTHJHLCC6DAI4MXOWKSDCUOII.gif&h=5deee971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【將軍澳】有貨van疑因撞向示威者而遭放火「私了」。夏家朗攝<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"e23b362f192ab751b421ae25e1edea670ab40ffa","tid":1709654,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:08:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"573f10f76c32e0d3d4beb96f3ff9f83dd632f01b","tid":1709654,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"貨van 底死"},{"pid":"935d5ddfcf8b4851cc767464925c43cbe342b521","tid":1709654,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />bb"},{"pid":"3c240cefeca8a8da75143db608d46b6963e1d18d","tid":1709654,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"今次私了條友好似幾傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13d695bc9122667fc39aa0c208728af85e45e81","tid":1709654,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"573f10f76c32e0d3d4beb96f3ff9f83dd632f01b","tid":1709654,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"貨van 底死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤"},{"pid":"c94df2d0535b2f453ff8b5cd06c17ef87912ca47","tid":1709654,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"55c2d0ddb1930fbe9ceef7945de8552fc414d33a","tid":1709654,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"935d5ddfcf8b4851cc767464925c43cbe342b521","tid":1709654,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />bb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"係， BB"}]}